ie Weinstein, Wilfried Wilms. Barbara Hales is Associate Professor of History at the University of Houston-Clear Lake. Mihaela Petrescu is Visiting Lecturer at the University of Pittsburgh. Valerie Weinstein is Assistant Professor of Women's, Gender, and Sexuality Studies and German Studies at the University of Cincinnati.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMotion picturesxHistoryy20th centuryzGermany. 0aMotion picturesxPolitical aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzGermany. 0aMotion picturesxSocial aspectsxHistoryy20th centuryzGermany. 4aFilm & Theatre. 4aGerman Literature. 4aModern History. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aEuropean history.  aGerman cinema.  aHitler.  aNazism.  aWorld War II.  aanthropology.  afilm scholarship.  afilm studies.  ahistory of film.  amedia studies.  asociology.  atwentieth century Germany.1 aFlaig, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrölich, Margrit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHales, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHales, Barbara, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHans, Anjeana K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHans, Anjeana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeinsohn, Bastian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHenkel, Brook, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohnson, Kevin B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLyons, Owen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcCormick, Richard W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichell, Kalani,